---
// Animated staircase background decoration. Positions itself absolutely in
// the bottom-right of its nearest positioned ancestor, so the parent should
// be `position: relative; overflow: hidden;`. One instance per page (uses a
// static SVG id for its GSAP shimmer animation script).
---

